title: Flipper - Gone Fishin' ... OOP PUNK
description:
Flipper&#039;s difficult second album, except nothing here sounds difficult at all... in fact, for Flipper, it sounds like business as usual.

Upon its release, &#039;Gone Fishin&#039; was frowned upon slightly, following cool on the heels of &#039;Generic&#039;. I personally think this album is a lost classic and at times even manages to eclipse their debut.

For some unknown reason, this album has never been reissued and has fallen into the void.

2. First The Heart
3. In Life my Friends
